Class AbstractMultiIndexQuantifierEliminator

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sri.ai.grinder.sgdpllt.core.solver.AbstractMultiQuantifierEliminator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractIterativeMultiIndexQuantifierEliminator, AbstractSGVET, DefaultMultiIndexQuantifierEliminator

    public abstract class AbstractMultiIndexQuantifierEliminator
extends java.lang.Object
implements MultiIndexQuantifierEliminator
    A MultiIndexQuantifierEliminator implementing interruption and debugging mechanisms.

    Extensions to this class must routinely invoke checkInterrupted() during its operation so as to allow interruption ordered by client code.

    braz
